comments: Ibaka (TOR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Dinwiddie's (BKN) path and as the pick concludes they briefly engage and disengage.
Jordan (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during Ibaka's (TOR) drive.
Dinwiddie (BKN) legally contest VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot.
Jordan (BKN) slightly turns as he sets a pick in Davis' (TOR) path. The contact is marginal and does not affect Davis' ability to defend.
Ibaka (TOR) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the play at the basket by LeVert (BKN).
Chandler (BKN) slightly extends two hands to Siakam's (TOR) side as he sets the pick. The contact is marginal and does not affect Siakam's ability to establish position during the pick.
Chandler (BKN) removes his forearm and makes marginal contact to VanVleet's (TOR) side on his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) places two hands on VanVleet (TOR) as VanVleet abruptly stops in Dinwiddie's path to set the pick, but he does not deliver any contact.
Chandler (BKN) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact to his initiated by Siakam (TOR).
Jordan (BKN) establishes himself in legal picking position in VanVleet's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Dinwiddie (BKN) places two hands on VanVleet (TOR) as he moves off-ball, but does not affect his FOM.
Replay review of the foul called on Chandler (BKN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Chandler (BKN) delivers contact to Siakam's (TOR) body during his driving shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contest LeVert's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
